slstatus-carbs
==============

Fork of suckless.org's slstatus, tuned for CARBS


Installation
------------

$ make
# make install


Notes
-----

This fork takes advantage of the dwm-extrabar patch
https://dwm.suckless.org/patches/extrabar/

There are programs and scripts used by Carbs (e.g PulseAudio, 
nightmode), you might want to tailor the script to your needs
if you are going to install this fork for some reason.
